    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> curry powder</strong> to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Press your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into the curry powder until well coated on both sides – this is your<strong> coated basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1721397034919-x200.jpg",
