            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the basa is cooking, combine your <strong>yoghurt</strong> with your <strong>green tomato chutney</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>green tomato yoghurt</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and shake off any excess water</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
