          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, add your <strong>spinach</strong> and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the pot</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until the spinach has wilted, then drain and reserve the pot</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1721397058994-x200.jpg",
