            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>curried basa</strong> with the <strong>saag aloo-style potatoes</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted almonds</strong> and <strong>nigella seeds</strong> over the basa</p><p>Add a dollop of <strong>green tomato yoghurt</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
